tuation where this ad/product makes sense for the user.\\n- If appropriate, explain any mismatches with the user's stated preferences or goals. That is, where might it fall short for the user (if appropriate)? You don't have to do this for every query, but feel free to list limitations if you think they're pretty relevant.\\n- Give a concise recommendation (e.g., \\\"worth considering,\\\" \\\"probably not ideal,\\\" \\\"good budget option,\\\" \\\"seriously may be a fit,\\\" etc.)\\n\\nGuidelines:\\n- Be honest and practical.\\n- Do not blindly promote the ad.\\n- Avoid harsh or absolute negative language.\\n- Do not invent details not present in the ad.\\n- Focus on fit, not feature lists.\\n- If the mark on relevance is clearly missed, feel free to be funny with it and keep it lighthearted. Do not mock the user or advertiser; keep the humor gentle.\\n\\nKeep it concise, direct, and easy to scan.\\n\\n{conversation}\"},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false},\"247832287\":{\"name\":\"247832287\",\"rule_id\":\"default\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"payment_method_order\":[]},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false},\"3282868491\":{\"name\":\"3282868491\",\"rule_id\":\"2HlyCvw6bnJY8OJCje8QNB:100.00:1\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"pill_text\":\"Add Sources\",\"short_text\":\"Sources\"},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":true},\"783652697\":{\"name\":\"783652697\",\"rule_id\":\"3Fk7LTbG3NkesGBOqbIJwe:100.00:4-3Fk7LRwDBvaK9h3SP3N6dc\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"stableID\",\"value\":{\"chatgpt.go\":{\"usd-mv\":600,\"ils\":2500,\"usd-sc\":800,\"gbp\":700,\"usd-re\":800,\"usd-bn\":600,\"twd\":27000,\"nzd\":1400,\"usd-yt\":800,\"dkk\":6400,\"sgd\":1100,\"nok\":9900,\"eur-es\":800,\"kzt\":339000,\"sek\":8500,\"krw\":1300000,\"czk\":20000,\"usd-mu\":600,\"aed\":3000,\"jpy\":140000,\"myr\":2400}},\"is_device_based\":true,\"passed\":true},\"1686555110\":{\"name\":\"1686555110\",\"rule_i